@startuml "Application State Machine - Diagram"

!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #ffffff
skinparam defaultFontName monospace
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam stateBorderColor #333333
skinparam stateBackgroundColor #fff4e6
skinparam arrowColor #333333

title "Application State Machine (AppMode)"

state "Normal" as Normal {
    Idle state
    Ready for user input
    Terminal display live
}

state "WaitingLLM" as WaitingLLM {
    Querying LLM backend
    Terminal frozen
    Animated throbber
}

state "AwaitingApproval" as AwaitingApproval {
    LLM provided command
    Waiting for y/n response
    Command displayed
}

state "AwaitingAnswer" as AwaitingAnswer {
    LLM asked question
    Waiting for text input
    Question displayed
}

' From Normal
Normal --> WaitingLLM : QueryLLM\n(user typed unknown command)

' From WaitingLLM
WaitingLLM --> Normal : LLMCompleted\n(LLM returned final result)

WaitingLLM --> AwaitingApproval : LLMRequestsApproval\n{ command, message }\n(LLM suggests dangerous cmd)

WaitingLLM --> AwaitingAnswer : LLMAsksQuestion\n{ question, options }\n(LLM needs clarification)

' From AwaitingApproval
AwaitingApproval --> Normal : UserResponded\n(user pressed y/n)

AwaitingApproval --> WaitingLLM : (resume with approval)\n[deferred - future feature]

' From AwaitingAnswer
AwaitingAnswer --> Normal : UserAnswered\n(user typed answer + Enter)

AwaitingAnswer --> WaitingLLM : (resume with answer)\n[deferred - future feature]

' From Any (Cancel)
Normal --> Normal : Cancel\n(idempotent)
WaitingLLM --> Normal : Cancel\n(Ctrl+C - abort LLM query)
AwaitingApproval --> Normal : Cancel\n(Ctrl+C - reject command)
AwaitingAnswer --> Normal : Cancel\n(Ctrl+C - abort question)

note right of Normal
    **Default state:**
    - User can type commands
    - PTY output displayed
    - Cursor visible
    - All input modes available
end note

note right of WaitingLLM
    **LLM Query in Progress:**
    - Terminal output frozen
    - Animated throbber shows wait state
    - User can press Ctrl+C to cancel
    - Streaming response display (future)
end note

note right of AwaitingApproval
    **Command Approval Needed:**
    - LLM command shown
    - Explanation/warning displayed
    - Waiting for y/n/Ctrl+C
    - Example: dangerous rm/dd commands
end note

note right of AwaitingAnswer
    **LLM Question Needs Answer:**
    - Question displayed
    - Free-text or multiple choice
    - Waiting for user input + Enter
    - Example: "Which file?"
end note

note bottom
    **State Machine Properties:**

    1. **Valid Transitions Only:**
       - can_transition_to(target) checks validity
       - Invalid transitions return error
       - Prevents corrupted state

    2. **Atomic Transitions:**
       - transition(event) consumes self + event
       - Returns new state or error
       - No intermediate states

    3. **Idempotent Same-State:**
       - Normal → Normal is valid (idempotent)
       - Allows safe retries

    4. **Cancel from Any State:**
       - Cancel event always → Normal
       - Provides user escape hatch
       - Ctrl+C triggers cancel

    5. **Direct Transitions Only:**
       - No chaining (Normal → AwaitingApproval forbidden)
       - Must go through WaitingLLM
       - Prevents accidental state bypass

    **Implementation:**
    AppMode enum variants store data:
    - AwaitingApproval { command, message }
    - AwaitingAnswer { question, options }
    Data consumed on transition (no clone)
end note

' Show state data
note left of AwaitingApproval
    pub enum AppMode {
        Normal,

        WaitingLLM,

        AwaitingApproval {
            command: String,
            message: String,
        },

        AwaitingAnswer {
            question: String,
            options: Option<Vec<String>>,
        },
    }
end note

@enduml
